@startuml
title UC08 - Enviar Cupom por E-mail

' Configuração visual melhorada
hide footbox
autoactivate off
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #374151
    LifeLineBorderColor #9CA3AF
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5FF
    ActorBorderColor #374151
    ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    DatabaseBorderColor #374151
    DatabaseBackgroundColor #F3E8FF
    BoxBorderColor #9CA3AF
    BoxBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    GroupBorderColor #9CA3AF
    GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    ActivationBorderColor #111827
    ActivationBackgroundColor #CFE3FF
    ParticipantPadding 28
    BoxPadding 10
    MessageAlign center
}
skinparam maxMessageSize 70

control "ResgateVantagemController
Micronaut" as Ctrl
queue "RabbitMQ
Fila de E-mail" as MQ
control "EmailConsumer" as Consumer
control "EmailService" as EmailService
collections "Gmail SMTP" as SMTP
actor Aluno as A
actor "Empresa Parceira" as E

Ctrl -> MQ: Publica evento
CupomResgatadoEvent
activate MQ
MQ --> Ctrl: Mensagem aceita
deactivate MQ

MQ -> Consumer: Entrega mensagem
activate Consumer
Consumer -> EmailService: enviarCupomAlunoEmpresa(evento)
activate EmailService
EmailService -> SMTP: Envia e-mail para aluno
activate SMTP
SMTP --> EmailService: OK
deactivate SMTP
EmailService -> SMTP: Envia e-mail para empresa
activate SMTP
SMTP --> EmailService: OK
deactivate SMTP
EmailService --> Consumer: E-mails enviados
deactivate EmailService
Consumer --> MQ: ACK da mensagem
deactivate Consumer

SMTP --> A: Recebe cupom por e-mail
SMTP --> E: Recebe aviso do resgate
@enduml
